# 🌐 Introduction to MERN Stack

This project is a simple HTML page that provides an introduction to the **MERN stack**, a popular JavaScript-based technology stack used to build full-stack web applications.

## 📄 Description

The HTML file includes:
- A short introduction to the MERN stack
- An ordered list of its core components:
  - MongoDB
  - Express.js
  - React
  - Node.js
- A sample image representing the MERN stack
- A link to MongoDB’s official website

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- External image placeholder
- Hyperlink to MongoDB site

